      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the advice. i'm already taking some ibuprofen but how much should i actually take if it's really bad? i don't want to keep running to the pharmacy every few hours. also, is it okay if i take it with a little bit of wine to help me sleep through the nap? it's been a stressful day lol.",
